OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777065070
OL,3,CAssisted dying bill expected to fail
OL,4,Cin House of Lords today
OL,6,FAn open letter to West Streeting from
OL,7,FAge UK, Hospice UK, and Marie Curie,
OL,8,Famong others, said it was a "critical
OL,9,Fmoment" to turn "shared ambition into
OL,10,Faction" and "deliver the improvements
OL,11,Fin palliative and end-of-life care"
OL,12,Furgently needed.
OL,14,F"The national conversation surrounding
OL,15,Fassisted dying has brought renewed
OL,16,Fattention to the urgent need for high-
OL,17,Fquality, accessible palliative and end-
OL,18,Fof-life care," it said.
OL,20,FWhere else have assisted dying bills
OL,21,Fbeen proposed?
OL,26,@pD@]OUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
