PN,31812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777065070
OL,3,CAssisted dying bill expected to fail
OL,4,Cin House of Lords today
OL,6,FThe Isle of Man became the first
OL,7,FBritish Isles to pass an assisted
OL,8,Fdying bill in 2025, but it has not yet
OL,9,Freceived Royal Assent, which it needs
OL,10,Fto become law.
OL,12,FThis usually takes around three to six
OL,13,Fmonths, but the Ministry of Justice
OL,14,Fhas halted the process, stating this
OL,15,Fmonth that more safeguards are needed
OL,16,Fin the legislation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777065070
OL,3,CAssisted dying bill expected to fail
OL,4,Cin House of Lords today
OL,6,FThe MoJ said it could not recommend
OL,7,Fthe bill for Royal Assent "at this
OL,8,Ftime", but that this should "not be
OL,9,Finterpreted as disallowing Royal
OL,10,FAssent".
OL,12,FJersey became the second British Isles
OL,13,Fto follow suit after passing its own
OL,14,Fbill in February, but it must also
OL,15,Ffollow the same process of being
OL,16,Fapproved by the King.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777065070
OL,3,CAssisted dying bill expected to fail
OL,4,Cin House of Lords today
OL,6,FBoth Crown dependencies have residency
OL,7,Frequirements for eligibility in their
OL,8,Fbills, with people needing to live in
OL,9,FJersey for a minimum of 12 months
OL,10,Fbefore they can apply for assisted
OL,11,Fdeath, and five years for the Isle of
OL,12,FMan.
OL,14,FA bill for assisted dying in Scotland
OL,15,Fwas rejected by Scottish Parliament in
OL,16,FMarch.
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/14
